    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215150/extras/387982617a69c290e6fbf5b845057f7a.avif?t=1729177015\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Streams Upon Memories is a psychological horror set in a surreal plane, questioning reality and what's really true. You wake up, not knowing who or even what you are, in an ethereal location, not sure what the hell you're doing up here.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215150/extras/893bd11b75e1d2cb7d3ddefc4c3f7a7b.avif?t=1729177015\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10k words.<br>8 CGs.<br>4 main different endings.<br>2 characters.<br>One location.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Original soundtracks.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Custom GUI.<br>Voice acting.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3215150/extras/b2b8ec652d858b12f088a2e10eee1746.avif?t=1729177015\" width=600 height=200 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Directed by Kashi Maadsen.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>ART</strong><br>Art lead, sprites and CGs<br>| Kashi Maadsen <br>Background artist<br>| Dax (Futotori) <br>GUI artist<br>| Anne (QuantumVelvelt) </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>PROGRAMMING</strong><br>Main programmer<br>| Samehawke <br>Co programmer, UI<br>| Beepsalt <br>Co programmer, Scene director<br>| Kashi Maadsen</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>WRITING</strong><br>Main Writer<br>| Aileen O'hearn <br>Co writer<br>| Jonathan Vogt <br>Editor<br>| Kashi Maadsen</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>MUSIC &amp; SOUNDS</strong><br>Main themes <br>| Dr. Ross Mitchell<br>Endings <br>| Melancholy Marionette<br>Sound effects, UI<br>| Zack</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>VOICE ACTING</strong><br>HUSK <br>| Pun<br>SYN <br>| Hydra<br>Singer, whispers, cries and screams.<br>| Eowyn Castel</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
